00:39:54.900 --> 00:39:57.400
So probability of
at least one head,

00:39:57.400 --> 00:40:02.685
it's not equal to the
probability of head

00:40:02.685 --> 00:40:07.656
for the penny plus the
probability of head

00:40:07.656 --> 00:40:13.130
for the dime, because we
know this is really 3/4,

00:40:13.130 --> 00:40:15.220
and this is 1/2, this is 1/2.

00:40:15.220 --> 00:40:19.190
