00:40:19.190 --> 00:40:22.890
So be careful.

00:40:22.890 --> 00:40:26.000
There's a lot of things you can
say quickly that are not true.

00:40:28.940 --> 00:40:33.230
So anyway, you really have
to consider the whole thing.

00:40:33.230 --> 00:40:36.304
And in the best case,
if you can enumerate

00:40:36.304 --> 00:40:38.720
what's going to happen, it's
very simple to add up things.

00:40:38.720 --> 00:40:41.380
Otherwise, you have to be
very careful with the algebra

00:40:41.380 --> 00:40:43.506
to make sure you add
all things correctly.

00:40:52.840 --> 00:40:55.000
