00:41:54.760 --> 00:42:00.636
Then these two things
just add up to 1.

00:42:00.636 --> 00:42:03.044
Is that all right?

00:42:03.044 --> 00:42:04.960
It's really saying the
probability of the dime

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:09.590
will do something if I
have a head for the penny.

00:42:09.590 --> 00:42:11.580
Is this all right?

00:42:11.580 --> 00:42:14.610
So you want to practice doing
little algebra things like this

00:42:14.610 --> 00:42:16.068
to make sure you
